.title Help: Adobe Type Manager(TM) Package
ABOUT THIS PACKAGE
The Adobe Type Manager package supports Adobe(TM) Type 1
scalable fonts for your display and printers.  This
package provides the files needed for the Adobe Type
Manager and the scalable (regular, bold, italic, and bold
italic) Utopia, Courier, Helvetica, and Times Roman fonts.

If you install this package, you must also install the
Graphics Utilities package.

EXITING THE PACKAGE SELECTION MENU
Press <Enter> to enter your selections and to return to the
Install Menu.
                                    (CONTINUED)
.page
EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Package Selection menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
